HEADWORD: Ripply
<hw>Rip"ply</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Having ripples;
<as>as, <ex>ripply</ex> water</as>; hence, resembling the sound of
rippling water; <as>as, <ex>ripply</ex> laughter; a <ex>ripply</ex>
cove.</as></def> <rj><au>Keats.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

